Device: Synaptics "Prometheus" (USB 06cb:009a; also 138a:0090/0097/009d)

Driver (userspace daemon): uunicorn
  https://github.com/uunicorn/python-validity
  License: MIT

fprintd-compatible DBus shim: open-fprintd
  (install alongside python-validity)

Protocol reverse engineering: nmikhailov, uunicorn and contributors
  https://github.com/nmikhailov/Validity90

Not a libfprint driver - a userspace driver daemon that registers with
open-fprintd so standard fprintd clients and pam_fprintd work.
